#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#: buildVars.py:12
msgid "WinForms .NET 4.8 Fixes"
msgstr "WinForms .NET 4.8 修复"

#. Add-on description
#: buildVars.py:14
msgid ""
"Consolidated accessibility fixes for .NET 4.8 WinForms applications, "
"including ComboBox navigation and MenuItem checked state reporting."
msgstr ""
"针对 .NET 4.8 WinForms 应用程序的辅助功能综合修复，包括读出组合框选中项改"
"变，读出菜单项选中状态和辅助功能描述信息。"

#. Brief changelog for this version
#: buildVars.py:18
msgid ""
"### 1.1.0\n"
"* Restored missing MenuItem description reporting by falling back to legacy "
"properties.\n"
"### 1.0.0\n"
"* Initial release.\n"
"* Fixed ComboBox selection reporting while collapsed (#17454).\n"
"* Fixed ToolStripMenuItem missing checked state reporting (#19335)."
msgstr ""
"### 1.1.0\n"
"* 修复了菜单项（MenuItem）说明信息（Description）缺失的问题。\n"
"### 1.0.0\n"
"* 初始版本。\n"
"* 修复了组合框在折叠状态下未读出选项改变的问题 (#17454)。\n"
"* 修复了 ToolStripMenuItem 未读出选中状态的问题 (#19335)。"
